### Create a new blog post
POST http://localhost:3000/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sample Post",
  "content": "This is a sample post content.",
  "author": "John Doe"
}

### Get all blog posts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/posts

### Get a single blog post by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/posts/{postId}  # Replace {postId} with an actual ID after creation

### Update a blog post by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/posts/{postId}  # Replace {postId} with an actual ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Post Title",
  "content": "Updated content.",
  "author": "Jane Doe"
}

### Delete a blog post by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/posts/{postId}  # Replace {postId} with an actual ID
